
                      An Eight Channel Logic Analyser.
                      --------------------------------


    Minimum Operating Requirements Are:-
    ------------------------------------

    1) A 1MB AMIGA A500, (originally designed for a 1.5MB A1000).
    2) Workbench 1.3x.
    3) An external floppy disk drive IS required.
    4) OCS.
    5) A television set.
    6) The mouse.
    7) The ~LHA~ program IS required for De-Archiving. This can be found
       in the ~util/arc~ drawer of AMINET.
    8) A hard disk drive is optional.
    9) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 3.1x or greater.
   10) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 1.2x or less.

